<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.10.3">
<l>muṭṭil palpōkat torutaṉi nāyakaṉ mūvula kukkuriya</l>
<l>kaṭṭiyait tēṉai yamutainaṉ pālaik kaṉiyaik karumputaṉṉai</l>
<l>maṭṭaviḻ taṇṇantu ḻāymuṭi yāṉai vaṇaṅki yavaṉṟiṟattu</l>
<l>paṭṭa piṉ ṉaiyiṟai yākilum yāṉeṉ maṉattu parivilaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Although he is the lord I am without affliction in my mind, after I have fallen</l>
<l>for him, bowing to the one solitary leader of many enjoyments without obstacle,</l>
<l>the sweetmeat that has the right to the three worlds, the honey, ambrosia, good milk, ripe fruit, sugarcane,</l>
<l>the one with a crown of cool tulsi on which the nectar[-blossoms] open.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
